<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
1. format
 1.1 ehplmn: List the sim card's ehplmn, it might have more than 1
 1.2 drop23Gpreferplmn: PLMN+PREFRAT
 1.3 PREFRAT: value indicates the single RAT, 0001 reserved,0010 reserved, 0100 LTE, 1000 SA.
     Note：multiple RATs is not supported to reduce complexity
2. Priority description considering equal signal quality:
   drop23Gpreferplmn is listed by priority in descending order, example
   45412+4,45403+4 indicates 45412 LTE has higher priority than 45403 LTE
   45412+8,45412+4 indicates 45412 SA has higher priority than 45412 LTE
   45412+4,45412+8 indicates 45412 LTE has higher priority than 45412 SA
-->
<!--
V1.0.0: Intial release,cmcc configure 4 prefer PLMN+PREFRAT, cu configure 5 PLMN+PREFRAT
-->
